Package: scLang
Type: Package
Title: A unified language for interacting with Seurat and SingleCellExperiment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person('Andrei-Florian', 'Stoica', 
      email='andreistoica@foxmail.com',
     role=c('aut','cre'),
     comment=c(ORCID='0000-0002-5253-0826'))
Description: scLang is a suite for package development for scRNA-seq analysis. 
    It offers functions—both getters and setters—that can operate 
    on both Seurat and SingleCellExperiment objects, intended to help 
    developers build tools compatible with both types of input.
